  Prisma SSL Inspection Bypass                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                           
Certificate pinning test — does Prisma MITM SSL? Check the cert chain on any HTTPS site:                                                                               
  DevTools → Security tab → View Certificate                                                                                                                         
  Is the root CA "Palo Alto Networks" or similar? If yes, SSL is inspected                                                                                             
TLS 1.3 encrypted client hello — may bypass inspection: prisma://flags/#encrypted-client-hello                                                                         
