  DevTools Persistence (Chromium-specific)                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                           
Sources → Overrides — set a local override folder. You can replace ANY remote file with a local version. Persists across page loads:                                   
    a. Sources tab → Overrides → Select folder → Allow                                                                                                                   
    b. Network tab → find the page's HTML → right-click → Override content                                                                                                 
    c. Inject keylogger into the HTML → it loads YOUR version every time                                                                                                   
Sources → Snippets — saved JS that persists across browser restarts. Run anytime:                                                                                      
    a. Sources → Snippets → New → paste keylogger → Ctrl+Enter to run                                                                                                      
    b. It stays there forever until manually deleted                                                                                                                       
Workspace mapping — link DevTools to a local folder, edit site files live                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                           
