  Highest-Impact Tests for the Report                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                           
  The findings that will matter most:                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                           
  1. prisma://policy — enumerate all Prisma policies (shows what they THINK is protected)                                                                                  
  2. Ctrl+S on restricted repos (already proven)                                                                                                                         
  3. DevTools Overrides — persistent code injection that survives page loads                                                                                               
  4. prisma://net-export — full network log export including filtered URLs                                                                                                 
  5. Console fetch + Blob download — bypass file type DLP                                                                                                                  
  6. clipboard.writeText() — bypass download block by copying to clipboard                                                                                                 
  7. QUIC/ECH/DoH flags — bypass SSL inspection                                                                                                                            
  8. Kill Prisma agent → fail-open test — if the browser works without the agent, game over                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                           
  Start with prisma://policy — that's your roadmap for everything Prisma is enforcing.
